summary:
ByteScout Spreadsheet SDK for .NET, ASP.NET, ActiveX/COM

Artifex Software Inc. (c) 2006-2023.

Bytescout Spreadsheet SDK reads, writes, calculates and converts spreadsheets (XLS, XLSX, ODS, CSV)

- Does not require Excel or Office installed;
- Formula calculation support (Excel style formulas);
- Reads XLS, XLSX, ODS (Open Office Calc), CSV formats;
- Writes XLS, XLSX, CSV, TXT, XML, JSON, HTML, PDF formats;
- Imports from and exports to JSON format;
- Supports cell formating, rich text, charts, images, borders, etc.;
- Supports legacy languages like Visual Basic 6, VBScript, JScript, ASP through ActiveX/COM interface;
- Command line utility is included for conversion of spreadsheet files from command line or .BAT files;
- And much more...

